Nootka 0.7.0 beta 1
===========================
===========BUILD===========
===========================

Requirements:
- Qt libraries (obviously)


UNDER LINUX
- Unpack tarball
- create some dir (f. e. "build") out of unpacked directory with sources
- go to build dir
- cmake ../nootka-0.7.0
- make
- make install (usually as root)

to remove (uninstall)
- make uninstall (usually as root)


UNDER WINDOWS
something similar as above but there is no install target
You have to manually copy picts and fonts directories to dir where 
nootka binary was created (src dir in build dir)

